<body>
    <h1>Upgrade Assigned Room Category</h1>
    <div class=3D"Section1">
        <p local-id=3D"7a788479ba5a"><strong>Component type:</strong> Actio=
n</p>
<p local-id=3D"648fae691669"><strong>Category:</strong> Reservations</p>
<h2 local-id=3D"8aea115792b6" id=3D"UpgradeAssignedRoomCategory-Overview">O=
verview</h2>
<p local-id=3D"ae05c27ef399">The <strong>Upgrade Assigned Room Category</st=
rong> action automatically upgrades guests to higher-category rooms based o=
n configurable upgrade paths and real-time room availability. You define wh=
ich room categories can be upgraded to which target categories, and the com=
ponent handles the rest =E2=80=94 checking availability, respecting buffer =
limits, and processing upgrades in order.</p>
<p local-id=3D"7b44b4deeb90">This is useful for maximizing occupancy and gu=
est satisfaction. For example, you can automatically upgrade guests from a =
Standard room to a Deluxe room when Deluxe rooms are available and underuti=
lized, while always keeping a configurable number of rooms in reserve for l=
ast-minute bookings.</p>
<p local-id=3D"f1f0ab17c1aa">The component produces two separate outputs: s=
uccessfully upgraded reservations are sent to the <strong>upgraded</strong>=
 port, and reservations that could not be upgraded are sent to the <strong>=
failed</strong> port with a reason explaining why.</p>
<hr local-id=3D"39221260-25bb-4548-bfdd-7b14e763a0ef">
<h2 local-id=3D"592d994c865c" id=3D"UpgradeAssignedRoomCategory-InputFields=
">Input Fields</h2>
<div class=3D"table-wrap">
<table data-table-width=3D"760" data-layout=3D"default" data-local-id=3D"47=
2b176f-27e9-4f93-aee3-2cb77af9bd4d" class=3D"confluenceTable">
<tbody>
<tr data-local-id=3D"884ec17b-06fb-4d8f-ba55-0bb2a110fdd1">
<th data-local-id=3D"90d4f449-8583-4ff1-95e2-d8abb6f09491" class=3D"conflue=
nceTh">
<p local-id=3D"60127d66a1ce">Field</p></th>
<th data-local-id=3D"020307b9-1bae-4dc1-a631-9490ee0a1ebf" class=3D"conflue=
nceTh">
<p local-id=3D"6faa46f7a9bd">Required</p></th>
<th data-local-id=3D"881f8844-7f84-4dfb-8c90-9561a9a09ca1" class=3D"conflue=
nceTh">
<p local-id=3D"ba5fecd26edc">Type</p></th>
<th data-local-id=3D"8d2a4463-bc2a-49a8-9513-00f69576e200" class=3D"conflue=
nceTh">
<p local-id=3D"e9b55b402de4">Description</p></th>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"8437b912-e296-4366-9eee-53c6c0d6493d">
<td data-local-id=3D"c9b599c8-c737-4e8f-bbc8-dd03cfdba0cb" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"8912cde00ae0"><strong>Reservation IDs</strong></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"40550d6c-f129-4447-b1d4-5eea9f612d59" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"2fb43f1808d2"><strong>Required</strong></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"6694c241-4973-4154-a678-413603170f6b" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"d18e4bf9aadf">Text (JSON array)</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"d23fc5ec-d461-40ce-bbbc-eb9edfea29db" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"c9eec52487dd">The list of reservation IDs to attempt upgrade=
s for, provided as a JSON array (e.g. <code>["abc-123","def-456"]</code>). =
Typically connected to the output of a <strong>Get Reservations</strong> co=
mponent using the variable picker. A single reservation ID string is also a=
ccepted and will be treated as a one-element list.</p></td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"9e31c46e-9549-420c-84ca-e2e81041db6e">
<td data-local-id=3D"a187b603-c816-4905-ada4-61195134d3fe" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"c29adfb12e75"><strong>Upgrade Paths</strong></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"194316ed-ff18-4df8-8543-64f54370bc3b" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"6f70c70bcd08"><strong>Required</strong></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"83e5bc9e-66ed-4229-b922-27baec9bd08b" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"80bf1314ee2a">Expression (list of rows)</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"19f864fd-fa41-468c-ad68-928621669493" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"7b6c7330d554">Defines the room upgrade mappings. Each row ma=
ps a <strong>From Room Category</strong> to a <strong>To Room Category</str=
ong>. The dropdowns are populated dynamically with the room categories conf=
igured in your property.</p>
<ul local-id=3D"54bbd221-064f-40e3-8cd5-82c25722dab1">
<li local-id=3D"80b98b0d-c022-4f35-a520-3c3324c78994">
<p local-id=3D"e9903043a2a4">Each source category (<em>From</em>) can only =
appear once to avoid conflicts.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"ee5a610b-ef9b-46be-8c79-178e9815d204">
<p local-id=3D"e6dc58ad8d64">Paths can be chained to form cascading upgrade=
s. For example, if you define Standard =E2=86=92 Deluxe and Deluxe =E2=86=
=92 Suite, a guest in a Standard room may be upgraded to Deluxe first, and =
if Deluxe is unavailable, the system will attempt Suite as a fallback.</p><=
/li>
</ul></td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"38ec0e12-0c14-484f-afe9-1df2911d501a">
<td data-local-id=3D"3589c059-b9ea-44d7-8c4a-55e6da00b6f4" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"00e905a73271"><strong>Availability Buffer</strong></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"01564065-bc01-4a9b-954b-193fd608ed4c" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"d8ce2a5882c0"><strong>Required</strong></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"d7267568-ec9f-4ba3-b3cf-06a688f5bba9" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"b0517b4dac2a">Number</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"69b40367-b3ee-4b7f-95d3-20f6b588ec22" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"247d3c70ca15">The minimum number of rooms to keep available =
in each target category. Upgrades are only performed while at least this ma=
ny rooms remain unoccupied in the target category. This ensures rooms are k=
ept in reserve for last-minute direct bookings. Set to <code>0</code> to up=
grade whenever any room is available.</p></td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"def4b120-d18e-4155-a90c-8810bfccf046">
<td data-local-id=3D"81d7f313-17b4-4450-bb9f-d0ce97356e41" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"7230f9ae58db"><strong>Max Rooms to Upgrade</strong></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"89d159ff-a7ff-49a9-b227-65d7282bd3bf" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"53049416074b"><strong>Optional</strong></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"26d4c5df-636a-4d4d-ae73-71a0ed238550" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"d8f1df33b18d">Number</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"64ab2d5a-3767-4fa3-8614-18de00a165b0" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"58be624e1185">The maximum number of rooms to upgrade in a si=
ngle run. Reservations are processed in the order they are provided; once t=
his cap is reached, remaining reservations are reported as failed with the =
reason <code>CAP_REACHED</code>. Leave empty to upgrade all eligible reserv=
ations with no cap. Minimum value: <code>1</code>.</p></td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"46721943-b1cc-4e3a-8cc8-2792b82786fe">
<td data-local-id=3D"4886b555-3969-41db-8ad5-0b515720cf47" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"829eaf3f6501"><strong>Per-Category Availability Overrides</s=
trong></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"4aad9a9b-3470-4d69-8f8e-6d2b1fe15510" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"5f002a9483b7"><strong>Optional</strong></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"2d611d8d-2217-4fa2-a9e7-c1795acc4787" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"1f54a2a1a572">Expression (list of rows)</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"c71834d8-22e2-419c-a62f-888e6641b1d5" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"474ee6431b10">Overrides the global <strong>Availability Buff=
er</strong> for specific room categories. Each row maps a <strong>Room Cate=
gory</strong> to a custom <strong>Availability Buffer</strong> value. For e=
xample, you might keep 3 Suites in reserve but only 1 Standard room. This f=
ield is found under the <strong>Advanced</strong> section.</p>
<ul local-id=3D"56b66ccc-b1d3-4fa6-a491-e9263a0700e8">
<li local-id=3D"1ca1a7ad-3f95-45a5-b5f0-0b47bbb18f39">
<p local-id=3D"7900a279e273">Each room category can only appear once.</p></=
li>
<li local-id=3D"48559cf2-74d7-46d1-8de9-1cd9de1dfe4b">
<p local-id=3D"e851a455011b">Categories not listed here use the global Avai=
lability Buffer value.</p></li>
</ul></td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
</div>
<p local-id=3D"c14fed48440d"><strong>Note:</strong> The <strong>Per-Categor=
y Availability Overrides</strong> field is located in the <strong>Advanced<=
/strong> section of the component settings, which is collapsed by default.<=
/p>
<hr local-id=3D"d0fd277c-14a7-4783-afb0-548b48d6e6eb">
<h2 local-id=3D"9516cf752ddc" id=3D"UpgradeAssignedRoomCategory-OutputPorts=
">Output Ports</h2>
<p local-id=3D"b4d75fa04a00">This component has three output ports: <strong=
>upgraded</strong>, <strong>failed</strong>, and <strong>cooldown</strong>.=
 Each port only fires when there is relevant data to send.</p>
<h3 local-id=3D"413f83e02b76" id=3D"UpgradeAssignedRoomCategory-UpgradedPor=
t">Upgraded Port</h3>
<p local-id=3D"aadec0953146">Fires when at least one reservation was succes=
sfully upgraded. The following output options are available:</p>
<div class=3D"table-wrap">
<table data-table-width=3D"760" data-layout=3D"default" data-local-id=3D"06=
68307d-0130-4802-a424-6e23a3e20bd0" class=3D"confluenceTable">
<tbody>
<tr data-local-id=3D"846fd077-08b5-4cbe-958e-785ad207eddb">
<th data-local-id=3D"24a7672c-c6f6-43c2-8645-944a7c5ab8d1" class=3D"conflue=
nceTh">
<p local-id=3D"e4a8b10f5cd5">Output Option</p></th>
<th data-local-id=3D"6d7c14fb-e152-4a8e-aadf-26dcbb6aae84" class=3D"conflue=
nceTh">
<p local-id=3D"84e175917d29">Type</p></th>
<th data-local-id=3D"acbdc133-e105-44f1-9ffe-dd1459701d7a" class=3D"conflue=
nceTh">
<p local-id=3D"af9b4417f45c">Description</p></th>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"31d60fb5-c5d8-4674-99a4-d2466dee40d6">
<td data-local-id=3D"3e9a99a0-0300-4b92-8e08-10eb42130016" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"72bb1602d966"><strong>Upgraded Reservations</strong></p></td=
>
<td data-local-id=3D"5ce90557-4f2d-48c3-a51b-add35ab1d4d4" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"ce34e64c042c">Array of objects</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"064ac652-a6ff-4c2b-a216-09fcbb352d23" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"fdfc03573f0b">The full list of successfully upgraded reserva=
tions. Each item contains the fields listed below.</p></td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"67abd21e-9c70-4e01-ab94-796327302f6b">
<td data-local-id=3D"4ee24ed5-e048-4687-b588-26ca658dc0fc" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"3a0d547032f7"><strong>Upgraded Count</strong></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"c3864175-22eb-47d3-bdc1-108841d46f76" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"ff920bbf69c1">Number</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"18529302-6a3e-4861-9219-b785bc696da8" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"aee9f7925b2b">The total number of reservations that were suc=
cessfully upgraded.</p></td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"313c5de6-9f64-49bd-8bbb-2ca7e5bc5cc9">
<td data-local-id=3D"bba9754e-3706-41e0-a3a6-f070070bb2d1" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"b14b23878a97"><strong>Upgraded Reservation IDs</strong></p><=
/td>
<td data-local-id=3D"cb649fa9-4d7f-4ffa-8d22-c0206a8bc5d1" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"054eca72242c">Array of strings</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"9ae5fd94-96f3-4036-bbf9-259dca7ee64e" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"191f6e76b125">A flat list of reservation IDs that were succe=
ssfully upgraded. Useful for passing to subsequent workflow steps.</p></td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
</div>
<p local-id=3D"d9a9c260e14d">Each item in the <strong>Upgraded Reservations=
</strong> array contains:</p>
<div class=3D"table-wrap">
<table data-table-width=3D"760" data-layout=3D"default" data-local-id=3D"99=
5cc6c8-a3a6-4118-9a3c-60eb5630afdc" class=3D"confluenceTable">
<tbody>
<tr data-local-id=3D"7fb110b4-9cfa-4b0b-a921-0333d0ac123b">
<th data-local-id=3D"2f735838-b172-4e62-b2c6-f9ea0a6a2f54" class=3D"conflue=
nceTh">
<p local-id=3D"7400540af21d">Field</p></th>
<th data-local-id=3D"766e2640-bd0d-4c09-8157-47193f5aa57a" class=3D"conflue=
nceTh">
<p local-id=3D"3d248b6e2dd2">Type</p></th>
<th data-local-id=3D"8a8533ed-4dcc-4d50-9f83-cf07f6958fa9" class=3D"conflue=
nceTh">
<p local-id=3D"d943f6642123">Description</p></th>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"8cbe0375-f08c-4862-938d-409f6b41a24f">
<td data-local-id=3D"046afc20-1a15-4d2b-9eb9-d23b6abe0f32" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"e2bd5c913d65"><strong>Reservation ID</strong></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"8e420db2-d8e3-49d3-aa37-e8590d8db4e0" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"7b2ec135badf">Text (GUID)</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"0b1c172a-5139-49f4-b664-00f3671a1f5a" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"4b7e363c4d35">The unique identifier of the upgraded reservat=
ion.</p></td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"ff916424-55bd-4af9-80b7-d5ab214c1cdd">
<td data-local-id=3D"c62a467b-6f9e-4dfc-9546-4ac61b654679" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"373fca99a54d"><strong>Guest ID</strong></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"9a6408d0-a6e0-4d80-9e01-19f9401b2362" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
