<h3 local-id=3D"2a9d65156ed1" id=3D"UpgradeAssignedRoomCategory-FailedPort"=
>Failed Port</h3>
<p local-id=3D"b6adb8ced54b">Fires when at least one reservation could not =
be upgraded. The following output options are available:</p>
<div class=3D"table-wrap">
<table data-table-width=3D"760" data-layout=3D"default" data-local-id=3D"1c=
f307b9-4bd6-40e1-8be0-498752ecd378" class=3D"confluenceTable">
<tbody>
<tr data-local-id=3D"97a8aa24-418f-4762-a4b2-0f242e5bfef2">
