nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"6f5c621be774">The full list of reservations that could not b=
e upgraded. Each item contains the fields listed below.</p></td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"225975f1-76f7-442f-aa0b-44647ef3f4c3">
<td data-local-id=3D"47f14d21-20bd-4ab0-be56-17930a95b410" class=3D"conflue=
